  "statement": {
    "markdown": "Create a responsive portfolio grid that can display a list of projects. The grid should have the following layout:\n\n### Requirements\n\n1. The grid should have 3 columns on desktop and 1 column on mobile.\n2. Each project card should have a title, description, and image.\n3. The grid should be responsive and work on different screen sizes.\n4. The project cards should have a hover effect that highlights the card when hovered.\n5. The project cards should be centered horizontally and vertically on the page."
  },
